Class PopulatorImpl<E extends KeyableBean>

  • gw.webservice.contactapi.abcontactapihelpers.impl.PopulatorImpl<E>

    public class PopulatorImpl<E extends KeyableBean>
implements BeanPopulator<E>, XmlPopulator<E>, _proxy_.gw.lang.reflect.gs.IGosuObject
    BeanPopulator and XmlPopulator implementation. This class sets and gets values in an XmlBackedInstance.
